Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the one week between then\Nand the end of summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.03,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それから 夏休みが終わるまでの一週間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...we didn't see Yozora at Neighbors Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:49.02,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夜空は隣人部に姿を見せなかった
